</code></pre>

<p class="info">As this is a relation there are allowed to be values in the set $A$ which donâ€™t have a mapping to a value in the set $B$. If this was a function and not a relation that wouldnâ€™t be allowed.</p>

<p class="info">This is a functional relation as each item in  $A$ only has <strong>one</strong> mapping to $B$.</p>
